data.description: Open the doors to your new private oasis.  Located on a 1.57 acre private lot, this property has seen a top to bottom renovation.  Enter the front door and immediately feel the updated color palate and meticulously appointed details.  The entrance has updated luxury plank flooring and new lighting.  Oversized dining room with new flooring, concrete chandelier, wainscoting, ship lap, fresh new paint palate and plenty of room for and extravagant dinner party or holiday gathering.  Several walls have been removed in the new kitchen to provide an open cooking area, New French doors for access to the outdoors, breakfast area and family room.  All new cabinetry, stainless, appliances, counter tops, island, lighting, wainscoting, back splash, hardware, flooring and paint colors.  Also, plenty of recessed lighting and counter space for all off your cooking needs.  Breakfast area with bow window grant tranquil outdoor views.  A spacious family room boasts new carpeting, custom build in's, fireplace, and new paint.  Large sliding door leads to the sunroom with its gorgeous wood ceiling, skylights, new lighting and flooring, and 14 floor to ceiling windows.  The sunroom also allows access to driveway and outdoor entertainment area.  Main level laundry/mudroom has new flooring, exterior access, and cabinetry for all of your storage needs.  There is a completely updated full bath on the main level with a walk-in shower, new vanity, shiplap and new flooring. The upper-level primary suite has luxurious new carpet, wooden ceiling fan and paint.  Primary bath has been completely remodeled with double raised vanity, cabinetry, lighting, flooring, ship lap and shower. Bedroom 2 has beautiful hardwood flooring, and plenty of closet space.  With its new calming color scheme bedroom 3 has beautiful new carpeting and plenty of closets.  bedroom 4 with is hardwood flooring is the perfect room for kids or guests.  There is an office on the upper level with hardwood flooring and new paint. Upper-level hallway has hardwood flooring. And there is more...completely redesigned lower level.  With access to the outdoor entertainment area and the new luxury plan flooring, new ceiling tiles, lighting, paint color, custom wall coverings, wood wrapped pillars, kitchen cabinetry and granite counter tops this will be enjoyed by family and friends. A bedroom suite awaits your guests and in-laws.  The bedroom has gorgeous new carpeting, ship lap and closet.  The new Jack & Jill bath with barn door access to family room has a raised vanity, new flooring, shiplap, walk in shower, beautiful hardware. Newly enclosed deck will serve all of your outdoor entertainment needs.  Char-broil outdoor, stainless kitchen, exposed beams, metal roofing, custom roll downs for seasonal use, ceiling fan and completely screened.  The newly resurfaced concrete pool will surely keep you cool on those hot summer days.  The pool has also been newly heated.  There is also a circular hot tub connected to the pool. Tiki bar with metal roof and bar seating has a newly installed Thor outdoor kitchen with pizza oven and rotisserie, wet bar and fridge.  New decking has extended the outdoor pool area to allow for seating areas and all of your entertainment needs.  Need to get away from all of the pool activities?  Follow the path to the private bungalow.  Covered porch, metal roof, screened in, exposed beans, solid wood wall, ceiling fan, custom rods for window treatments and privacy. Take the wooden bridge and enjoy a fire at the custom pergola with 5 wooden swings. The rear wooded yard offers complete privacy. There is also a side yard for you garden, lawn shed, NEW home generator, and new house roof within the last 5 years. The owner has transformed this home into a private oasis or an entertainment mecca.  Schedule your showing today and you will be overwhelmed by the details and beauty of this custom property.
